{"tid":1573100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金澤培：警方已透過法庭手令取得「8.31」太子站事件的錄影副本","createTime":"2019-09-16T01:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T02:15:05.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f787a7b2b34e350d142924a1685942e49ae1246f","tid":1573100,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:14:40.000Z","msg":"港鐵行政總裁金澤培表示，為應付跳閘等違反《港鐵附例》行為，近日已增加人手，並安排包括尼泊爾裔保安等組成的200人特遣隊處理，至於治安問題則由警方負責。<br />\n<br />\n他昨出席電視節目時說，警方已透過法庭手令取得「8.31」太子站事件的錄影副本，強調不應由港鐵單方面公開閉路電視片段，以免影響警方調查，但他說，所有合資格的團體可透過法律途徑取得相關片段。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5%e8%a8%ad%e7%89%b9%e9%81%a3%e9%9a%8a-%e6%87%89%e4%bb%98%e8%b7%b3%e9%96%98-188907\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2590%25b5%25e8%25a8%25ad%25e7%2589%25b9%25e9%2581%25a3%25e9%259a%258a-%25e6%2587%2589%25e4%25bb%2598%25e8%25b7%25b3%25e9%2596%2598-188907&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xRnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=11327ab3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5%e8%a8%ad%e7%89%b9%e9%81%a3%e9%9a%8a-%e6%87%89%e4%bb%98%e8%b7%b3%e9%96%98-188907</a>"},{"pid":"4cc1f8e1a3f959152c2dd017e81f6d4f2e487c92","tid":1573100,"uid":34869,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:16:28.000Z","msg":"比狗cut完先播?"},{"pid":"f7bc6d6358a7272e33c3975614a0c4d220cb35a8","tid":1573100,"uid":109780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:17:12.000Z","msg":"仆街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e28b0328f3d81615cc57bd621623d8ac706068e","tid":1573100,"uid":146257,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:18:18.000Z","msg":"你自己班狗係站入面最清楚事實 仲拎埋cctv <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cca795711fb9277fe3c6a3a080cdcfc3b33e150","tid":1573100,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislik